Package: rnsf
Title: Interface to the NSF Grants API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Brian", "O'Meara", email = "omeara.brian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Uses the United States' National Science Foundation (NSF) API (https://www.research.gov/common/webapi/awardapisearch-v1.htm) to download info on awards (grants for funding science). Also includes functions for visualizing and analyzing the data.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports: jsonlite,
    plyr,
    wordcloud,
    tm
Suggests: testthat
